# Selebox All-In-One — Project Context

_Last updated: April 26, 2026_

## Overview
Selebox is a social platform with native video features. The website integrates with a mobile app (built on Appwrite) and uses Bunny.net for video hosting/streaming.

## Stack
- **Database / Auth:** Supabase
- **Video hosting:** Bunny.net (Stream)
- **Video playback:** HLS.js (inline in feed)
- **Mobile app backend:** Appwrite
- **Edge Functions:** Supabase Edge Functions (e.g., `bunny-delete`)

## Routes / Features
- **Home feed** — posts include video entries, rendered inline via HLS.js, linked through `video_id`
- **Profile** — feed/profile queries include `videos(...)` join
- **Creator Studio** — `#studio` route; full table view, stats, edit modal, delete action
- **Video uploads** — create posts in home feed automatically

